{"tid":2511970,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中央：檢測發現騰訊、百度旗下地圖等33款 App 違法收集使用個人資料","createTime":"2021-05-01T10:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T00:58:06.000Z","uid":99885,"like":59,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"e9921aa675924eac6d17c707c0dc6974e268d6c3","tid":2511970,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 國家互聯網信息辦公室對輸入法、地圖導航等常見類型公眾大量使用的部分 App 的個人資料收集使用情況,進行檢測,最新通報輸入法等33款 App 違法違規收集使用個人資料,涉及搜狗輸入法、高德地圖、百度(09888)的百度地圖、騰訊(00700)旗下騰訊地圖等。<br />\n<br />\n針對是次檢測發現的問題,中央網信辦要求相關 App 運營者要在本通報發布之日起10個工作日內完成整改,並將整改情況向其辦網絡數據管理局報告,逾期未完成整改將予以處置。"},{"pid":"3e0d40a46d10e6f1c7f233943ffdb53789b678da","tid":2511970,"uid":5178,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"扯貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93deff57ab31846abaa6dde59e195f1c5537f612","tid":2511970,"uid":3508,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"多謝笑話"},{"pid":"c297d8bf142adfd9f3de632ddc150817b2feebc0","tid":2511970,"uid":13782,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:26:01.000Z","msg":"又揾借口罰錢回血啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad98e210cbee4ba9476a8e552b6408ce08fbc107","tid":2511970,"uid":123774,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:26:40.000Z","msg":"收集數據唔記上繳中央"},{"pid":"f626e255070cdd244bfbf6f25cdb02b90e51d122","tid":2511970,"uid":166474,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"司那咁重視私隱嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfd2d447d0d56865004e9e2b0adbb4fce81e13c","tid":2511970,"uid":178875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"今個月未交數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1dad2cc6400a109d8d96c074cb774ccea771bb","tid":2